      ],"description": "The HP E45c G5 DQHD Curved Monitor (6N4C1AA) is engineered to enhance your workspace with its expansive 44.5-inch diagonal display, delivering a Dual QHD (5120 x 1440) resolution that effectively replaces dual 24-inch QHD monitors. Its 1500R curvature provides an immersive viewing experience, while the VA panel ensures vibrant visuals with a 3000:1 contrast ratio and 99% sRGB color gamut coverage.\nKey Features:\n\n\nExpansive Display: 44.5-inch diagonal screen with Dual QHD (5120 x 1440) resolution offers ample space for multitasking and enhances productivity.\n\n\nHigh Refresh Rate: 165Hz refresh rate combined with AMD FreeSync™ Premium technology ensures smooth visuals, reducing screen tearing and input lag.\n\n\nVersatile Connectivity: Equipped with HDMI 2.1, DisplayPort 1.4, dual USB-C ports supporting up to 100W power delivery, and a built-in KVM switch for seamless transitions between two computers.\n\n\nEnhanced Comfort: Features ergonomic adjustments including height, tilt, and swivel, along with HP Eye Ease technology and an ambient light sensor to reduce eye strain during extended use.\n\n\nIntegrated Audio: Built-in dual 3W speakers provide clear audio, eliminating the need for external speakers and reducing desktop clutter.\n\n\nUpgrade your workspace with the HP E45c G5 DQHD Curved Monitor, designed to deliver immersive visuals, versatile connectivity, and ergonomic comfort, making it an ideal choice for professionals seeking efficiency and style.","sku": "6N4C1AA","brand": {
